    "title": "10 Ways SPAM Taught Us to Focus Our Attention &sect; 1",
    "title_plain": "10 Ways SPAM Taught Us to Focus Our Attention &sect; 1",
    "content": "<blockquote><p>DIGITAL WILL BE GIVING A PRODUCT PRESENTATION OF THE NEWEST MEMBERS OF THE DECSYSTEM-20 FAMILY; THE DECSYSTEM-2020, 2020T, 2060, AND 2060T.  THE DECSYSTEM-20 FAMILY OF COMPUTERS HAS EVOLVED FROM THE TENEX OPERATING SYSTEM AND THE DECSYSTEM-10\u00a0COMPUTER ARCHITECTURE.  BOTH THE DECSYSTEM-2060T AND 2020T OFFER FULL ARPANET SUPPORT UNDER THE TOPS-20 OPERATING SYSTEM. THE DECSYSTEM-2060 IS AN UPWARD EXTENSION OF THE CURRENT DECSYSTEM 2040 AND 2050 FAMILY. THE DECSYSTEM-2020 IS A NEW LOW END MEMBER OF THE DECSYSTEM-20 FAMILY AND FULLY SOFTWARE COMPATIBLE WITH ALL OF THE OTHER DECSYSTEM-20 MODELS.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>You&#8217;ve just read the <!-- a href=\"http:\/\/www.templetons.com\/brad\/spamreact.html#msg\" -->very first spam message<!-- \/a -->. <strong>(REFERENCE ICON) FURTHER READING <a href=\"http:\/\/www.templetons.com\/brad\/spamreact.html#msg\">Reaction to the DEC Spam of 1978<\/a> <\/strong>Sent by Carl Gartley on behalf of Gary Thuerk,  this message went to several hundred ARPANET members on May 3, 1978. The message violated the until-then standard practice of e-mailing people individually (ah, those were the days!) and annoyed a whole lot of ARPANET users. It also sold some computers. And thus, the era of spam marketing was born.<\/p>\n",
    "excerpt": "DIGITAL WILL BE GIVING A PRODUCT PRESENTATION OF THE NEWEST MEMBERS OF THE DECSYSTEM-20 FAMILY; THE DECSYSTEM-2020, 2020T, 2060, AND 2060T. THE DECSYSTEM-20 FAMILY OF COMPUTERS HAS EVOLVED FROM THE TENEX OPERATING SYSTEM AND THE DECSYSTEM-10\u00a0COMPUTER ARCHITECTURE. BOTH THE DECSYSTEM-2060T &hellip; <a href=\"http:\/\/book.hyko.org\/1970-09-01\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a>",
