    "title_plain": "10 Ways You Can Help to Build the Internet &sect; 3",
    "content": "<div id=\"attachment_13446\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\" style=\"width: 310px\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.alexandrasamuel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/04\/SRI-PacketVan-SourceUnknown.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-13446\" src=\"http:\/\/www.alexandrasamuel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/04\/SRI-PacketVan-SourceUnknown-300x210.jpg\" alt=\"Map shows connections made by SRI packet van experiment\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" \/><\/a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Network map for packet van demonstration<\/p><\/div>\n",
