    "content": "<div class=\"wp-caption alignright\" style=\"width: 385px\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.history.navy.mil\/photos\/images\/g20000\/g27797c.htm\"><img src=\"https:\/\/img.skitch.com\/20110331-xe1r8j73c4kjyd74xnf53j4pfs.jpg\" alt=\"Woman using ditto machine in 1943\" width=\"375\" height=\"296\" \/><\/a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">No, I&#8217;m not this old. But talking with a 25-year-old about dittos sure makes me feel like it. (Photo from the Navy Historical Center.)<\/p><\/div>\n",
