    "content": "<p>Or more recently: Mosaic, usenet, magnolia, Friendster, Pets.com, Napster, geoCities, Flooz, SixDegrees, Digg, eToys, MySpace, the WELL, Google Wave. Sure, some of them are still around, but even they are ghosts of their former selves.<\/p>\n",
