    "title": "Finding Our Online Elders &sect; 2",
    "title_plain": "Finding Our Online Elders &sect; 2",
    "content": "<p>In most societies, that role is played by elders: people who by virtue of their age, wisdom or accomplishments serve as our mentors and models. These are the folks who&#8217;ve been around the block, found their way past obstacles and made some kind of meaningful contribution. Their role as elders can be completely informal, but it&#8217;s often institutionalized through a position of authority or honorific title.<\/p>\n",
