    "title_plain": "Finding Our Online Elders &sect; 7",
    "content": "<p>It&#8217;s this larger notion of the online moderator &#8212; the online facilitator &#8212; that gives us the online equivalent of the offline elder. These are people whose role is not only referee our online conversations, but to help us see what they can become; to help us become the kind of online society we want and need.<\/p>\n",
