    "title": "7 Rules for Rule-Breakers &sect; 1",
    "title_plain": "7 Rules for Rule-Breakers &sect; 1",
    "content": "<p>The first thing I ever stole online was the voice of Homer Simpson. No sooner had I heard a friend&#8217;s computer replace the system beep with a &#8220;D&#8217;oh!&#8221; then I knew I had to have Homer on my machine. Using the office intranet I snagged the sound file and installed in on my own computer&#8217;s sound manager. <em>D&#8217;oh! <\/em>I was now a thief.<\/p>\n",
    "excerpt": "The first thing I ever stole online was the voice of Homer Simpson. No sooner had I heard a friend&#8217;s computer replace the system beep with a &#8220;D&#8217;oh!&#8221; then I knew I had to have Homer on my machine. Using &hellip; <a href=\"http:\/\/book.hyko.org\/1970-04-01\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a>",
