    "title": "7 Rules for Rule-Breakers &sect; 10",
    "title_plain": "7 Rules for Rule-Breakers &sect; 10",
    "content": "<p>What worries me is that all too often, it isn&#8217;t a conscious choice. We break rules online when it&#8217;s easy, when we know how, when our friends are doing it. We follow rules when we are scared about getting caught, when it feels like too much trouble to defy them, when we don&#8217;t know a way around them.<\/p>\n",
    "excerpt": "What worries me is that all too often, it isn&#8217;t a conscious choice. We break rules online when it&#8217;s easy, when we know how, when our friends are doing it. We follow rules when we are scared about getting caught, &hellip; <a href=\"http:\/\/book.hyko.org\/1970-04-10\/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a>",
