    "content": "<p>Instead, we are as scarcity-driven as ever. Sure, talk of abundance has caught on, whether in <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">business circles<\/span> or <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">personal growth<\/span> or in my own community of <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">nonprofit tech<\/span>. But when you look at how people behave online, we seem as scarcity-driven as ever.<\/p>\n",
